cocktail that deserves its place next to the Caipirinha! Always Shaken or Blended, this \'milkshake style\' is quite uniquely creamy and fruity with the Brazilian national spirit Cachaca kicking through. ','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(80%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(20%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(237,'Pineapple & Lime Mocktail','NON-ALC','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F433f754e7c37d0aeeb1fe0c1c3588134c2ac77235cfa3460ddbd0688798076e7%3F&w=3840&q=75','A tangy, long and refreshing \'mock-tail\' that has a zing and pizazz about it. The rich flavours of the pineapple balanced perfectly with the sweet agave and lengthened with tonic. ','width: calc(0%);','width: calc(80%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(20%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(238,'Aviation','GIN','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F0a88760ddd32115f1f3ed5dd14f529e673853daf643bf1c4239a642f51ee5b44%3F&w=3840&q=75','The crème de violette adds a subtle floral character and light purple / blue colour to this Gin straight up cocktail, inspired by the Early romantic days of aeronautics ','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(80%);','width: calc(40%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(239,'Penicillin','SCOTCH WHISKY','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F363c32afaed89659ecbaaabcc5cf1f80cead43927f381eff468c337f87f472ce%3F&w=3840&q=75','Originally created in 2005 by Sam Ross in NYC, this has quickly become a bartender favorite due to its sweet-sour balance and the use of two different Scotch\'s! ','width: calc(100%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(60%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(240,'Whisky Cuba Libre','WHISKEY','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Fa3cd086f6b39fda5e33d9b1c9292758f5639b137f3030282ef2c27eb534e1a26%3F&w=3840&q=75','It doesn\'t get much simpler (and refreshingly tasty) than the classic Cuba Libre, which was popularised in Havana in 1900! Cuban rum mixed with Coca-Cola and fresh lime, simple.','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(0%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(241,'Limoncello Spritz','APERITIVO BITTERS','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F252c1370b73198c4a62f3b090e62126d25bac6850fe2c3ef7c2bacf1fbdad817%3F&w=3840&q=75','A trendy twist of the classics spritz and a new favorite for many. Dare to try this Italian twist, where this traditional Italian liquor provides a twist of color, sweetness and citrus explosion. Ideal for brunch time or welcome drink.','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(20%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(40%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(242,'Sex On The Beach','VODKA','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F689a96a435fe8f3c8a48183a5de5022aa8e97829df4ccc196ce5601814c541e9%3F&w=3840&q=75','The true 1980\'s disco cocktail that keeps on giving! It\'s long, fruity, sweet and has a kick to it. Bartender Tip: If you\'re going to go retro, go the whole hog and get those umbrellas and flamingos out!','width: calc(20%);','width: calc(100%);','width: calc(0%);','width: calc(0%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(243,'Tatanka','NON-ALC','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F780a5cb0229e4b43f9958bfc997936bae18384acb4bcf2b0e52a0ae30fbc91c8%3F&w=3840&q=75','This Polish drink takes its name from the film \'Dances With Wolves\'. Tatanka is a Native American word for buffalo and refers to the Bison grass flavored vodka the cocktail is based on, sweet and refreshing on a lazy summer afternoon. The natural sugar from the juice, combined with the botanical and nutty flavors from the vodka, is reminiscent of a fluffy apple pastry that doesn’t weigh you down. ','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(20%);','width: calc(0%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(244,'Lynchburg Lemonade','TENNESSEE WHISKY','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F17f5a42a470ef97683f17fe69da54fc6113a4d1db52f157717ab78e133f3ae73%3F&w=3840&q=75','Created for Jack Daniels at their Distillery in Lynchburg, it brings out the Whiskey\'s characteristic flavors with the citrus tang and fizzy lemonade. ','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(40%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(245,'Pimm\'s Cup','APERITIVO LIQUEUR','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Ff3814b3475748224fdc2b122911dc7ad94347e16ed1c56ca8601e2d1638b7565%3F&w=3840&q=75','A British summertime stable, drunk in every Pub garden and BBQ across the land! Almost a fruit salad in a glass, its all about the fresh easygoing flavours. ','width: calc(20%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(0%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(246,'French Martini','VODKA','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F10c4a4ad32d343c3ae4533f53b2e3ccd99b3d93d9bfb40136ccef3158890606e%3F&w=3840&q=75','Not actually French. Or actually a Martini for that matter. Yet, this fruity, foam topped straight up cocktail works well. A strong vodka base, an exoticness from the pineapple juice and a punch from the Chambord shake together for a scrumptious French Martini. ','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(80%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(20%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(247,'Bramble','GIN','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Ffab12174a74817faea6adf7372882ed14e557e13d4b3931df9a610fb66c6aba3%3F&w=3840&q=75','Created by Dick Bradsell in London in the 1980s, this ever-popular Cocktail has become a true classic with a Gin sour heart and an imaginative drizzle of blackberry liquor over the top of crushed ice for that sweet-sour finish. ','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(0%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(248,'Old Fashioned','COCKTAIL BITTERS','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Ffe0d45c48a54ff33aaa469e6129049284a38158ff5b32fddc108f8260fabfcf3%3F&w=3840&q=75','It may be Old by name, but this particular recipe and method is relatively modern and has become one of the most ordered cocktails in top bars Globally!','width: calc(100%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(20%);','width: calc(80%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(249,'Porn Star Martini','VANILLA VODKA','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F00bdb749bbe1f27962b5ffc9d20ed0d390220b8b1f62b0569fb5b45bbdfe2dc9%3F&w=3840&q=75','You can either love or hate the name of the cocktail, created by Douglas Ankrah in London, but its fruity bold flavour is undeniable. You\'ll be surprised how well they go down. ','width: calc(80%);','width: calc(80%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(20%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(250,'Gin Fizz','GIN','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F1e97872dc585e930f6b4607e20ac315b9bc849b30b34c0d4dac770813eaec5fc%3F&w=3840&q=75','Practical identical to a Tom Collins, this is a classic formula that stands the test of time. Gin, lemon and sugar shaken hard and topped with a fizz of soda. Bartender Tip: This classic recipe allows for easy twisting...why not experiment with a splash of your favourite puree or fruit liqueur.','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(0%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(251,'Whisky Sour','WHISKY','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F7460337a09cf18cf698165adba8195d33642d5347f171875e661b4b03d9426ad%3F&w=3840&q=75','An absolute classic, stemming from the mid 1800\'s, is a story in cocktail balance. The strong whisky notes cutting through the harmony of lemon/sugar with a kick from the bitters and foamy texture the shaken egg white gives ','width: calc(80%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(40%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(252,'Bloody Mary','VODKA','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F22b39199e1cee35cc3eed6a0f9cb778a318d79d1fc7cafae9d18ea4c2d8c66ad%3F&w=3840&q=75','The Bloody Mary will soon celebrate it\'s 100th Birthday...100 years of being the go to cocktail for brunches, on aeroplanes and for hangovers!! A unique Savoury cocktail with a true multi-flavour mix of sweet, sour, salt, umami and spicy! ','width: calc(80%);','width: calc(0%);','width: calc(20%);','width: calc(60%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(253,'Rum Old Fashioned','COCKTAIL BITTERS','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Fd3a97df0fa5f41a3f5f95036c6984be1afbb6543b36297e41bbc949ce61e22d4%3F&w=3840&q=75','A Twist on the classic Old Fashioned which traditionally uses Whiskey, this Rum variant adds slightly sweeter more rounder characteristics. ','width: calc(100%);','width: calc(80%);','width: calc(20%);','width: calc(60%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(254,'Madras','VODKA','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Fbdd43ac28f2bac1d58fa79b7f4f50b5aa16717a69ef66e410b1e1eed9e13556d%3F&w=3840&q=75','The Madras is a \'Sea Breeze\' cocktail, replacing the Grapefruit juice with Orange juice making it the slightly sweeter cousin. ','width: calc(20%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(20%);','width: calc(20%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(255,'Pisco Sour','PISCO','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Fa161508a1560f69d13e9f6c59366f6dbcf796532a77b0011bedbea29af4d173d%3F&w=3840&q=75','Leave the arguing of Peruvian or Chilean aside and just agree that this is a stunning cocktail with a light fluffy texture and great aromatic flavours.','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(20%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(256,'Black Russian','VODKA','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Fe2ed9e036c8f1e3c167f7837f00b01daf84e0bc4389ea1a0ad874bd3ba442d35%3F&w=3840&q=75','Created at the start of the Cold War by Gustave Tops, a bartender at Hotel Metropole in Brussels serving Perle Mesta, the American ambassador to Luxembourg. This original mix of Russian vodka and dark coffee liquor is simple to make but packs a punch. Add milk/cream to make a White Russian! ','width: calc(80%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(0%);','width: calc(40%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(257,'Piña Colada','COCONUT RUM','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Fd79029bdf26a8251cfca2c66c9254af2ea43662494567afd05bc86dce852f543%3F&w=3840&q=75','What could be more tropical than the exotic mix of Rum, pineapple and coconut?? Created in the middle of the 20th Century, it has been enjoyed on holidays and pool sides ever since. ','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(80%);','width: calc(20%);','width: calc(0%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(258,'Moscow Mule','VODKA','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F33d3abfa161f184d362be864111282c342d25077c78cad249a3ceda88d693240%3F&w=3840&q=75','내용없음','내용없음','내용없음','내용없음','내용없음',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(259,'Dry Martini (Bond)','VODKA','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Fd0df5b49e5a059c0a2324fa9124a82529aa50ff4cf795ff404dfcfce9d58fe13%3F&w=3840&q=75','Although popular before Bond, Ian Fleming\'s hero brought this straight up cocktail into the mainstream awareness lifting it to cult status. Shaking a Martini vs. Stirring will make it slightly colder, slightly more diluted and with an icy cloudiness. ','width: calc(100%);','width: calc(0%);','width: calc(0%);','width: calc(60%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(260,'Mango & Chili Margarita','TEQUILA','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F364a31b361efef22b5fb154bc4bcf335fcd5efc5e57b48d4eeffb63c88c3174d%3F&w=3840&q=75','There are several theories of where the margarita first originated and we’re not sure which one is true! But the most popular is that it was created in 1938 by Carlos ‘Danny’ Herrera at his restaurant in Tijuana, Mexico. It’s thought that he created it for a customer who was allergic to all hard alcohol except tequila but wanted something more than just a shot. This beautiful twist of mango and chili gives us color and spice to a classic of the summer cocktail bar. ','width: calc(80%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(20%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(261,'Daiquiri','LIGHT RUM','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Fa9ce5bb8de7a88167825a099e175545284739050bae77c1a19fe6ab71293e350%3F&w=3840&q=75','An absolute classic, stemming from the small mining town of Daiquiri in Cuba. The simple mix of the Rum, lime and sugar has sublime balance, hence its popularity Worldwide. ','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(0%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(262,'Negroni Sbagliato','APERITIVO BITTERS','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Fa78b1c8839b260dbd7e84d111fbaa87cb64601abd4f45e15a57f57680e10f4ac%3F&w=3840&q=75','Sbagliato means \'the wrong\' Negroni. In 1972, Mirko Stocchetto at Bar Basso in Milano added sparkling wine instead of Gin to Negroni. It was then that he realized that this variation made sense and this humble mistake led him to create one of the classic cocktails that is still enjoyed today around the world. ','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(80%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(80%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(263,'Mezcal Margarita','MEZCAL','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F3ff3273331ffbce43e9cbc7bceb613fc57ae798289df937b2a6a8f28f565e2dc%3F&w=3840&q=75','In Tijuana, a waiter was \'captivated\' by the beauty of a young dancer named Margarita Carmen Cansino and created this cocktail in her honor. This beauty would later become one of the most famous actresses in Hollywood, Rita Hayworth. Here is a new version of this classic, revisioned with Mezcal. ','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(60%);','width: calc(20%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(264,'Hanky Panky','GIN','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F5feb127a4e543dbd9ac3cf51de9d066d541da1161aa1d627417c798406f52094%3F&w=3840&q=75','Created by Ada Coleman, the first Bar Manager at the American Bar in the Savoy, London. Her customer explained \'By Jove! That is the real hanky-panky!\' . This strong and bitter cocktail is popular with Negroni fans. ','width: calc(100%);','width: calc(20%);','width: calc(20%);','width: calc(80%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(265,'Aperol Spritz','APERITIVO BITTERS','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F5304371a8e80dd0c2930081eabfcbd4703b4a283ea6cc3b657fb2302f9a2e0cf%3F&w=3840&q=75','Created in 1919 and has become a modern classic that has taken the world by storm the last few years! A refreshing long drink, perfect for warmer months and enjoyed best with friends.','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(40%);','width: calc(0%);','width: calc(40%);',NULL,'2023-10-01 04:35:42'),(266,'Caipirinha','CACHACA','https://cocktailclub.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcocktailclub.fra1.digitaloceanspaces.c